#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.2.rst:31
msgid ""
"Added function pytest.freeze_includes(), which makes it easy to embed pytest "
"into executables using tools like cx_freeze. See docs for examples and "
"rationale. Thanks Bruno Oliveira."
msgstr ""

